title: NaCl-templated synthesis of soybean-derived nitrogen-rich mesoporous carbon material: iron phthalocyanine integration for four-electron oxygen reduction
content:
Sustainable Energy Fuels, 2024, 8,4344-4354
DOI: 10.1039/D4SE00745J, Paper
Vikram Rathour, Smita Singh, Varsha Singh, Devesh Kumar Singh, Vaibhav Verma, Piyush Kumar Sonkar, Vellaichamy Ganesan
Mesoporous carbon, synthesized from soybean using NaCl as a template, is further integrated with iron phthalocyanine. This combination yields a material (FePc@SN950) with enhanced selectivity for the four-electron oxygen reduction process.
